    "description": "Joe has been trapped deep in the mine after an earthquake. Help him navigate the dark tunnels of the mine and face its dangers until he finds the exit.<br><br>He explores the mine by jumping to avoid obstacles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005170/extras/e2758aa37442b7a1dc8f6d335ba53c09.avif?t=1741545119\" width=524 height=396 /></span><br><br>Find objects to advance. Pickaxes to defend yourself, medkits to recover energy, gold to collect and exchange for health and access cards to open doors and advance.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005170/extras/9d49ee73bad80ae1592844538ae583d4.avif?t=1741545119\" width=528 height=394 /></span><br><br>Avoid or defeat tunnel threats. Use spikes to kill enemies or simply jump over them to avoid them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005170/extras/21a8e86e877c043407291f2ef48125ab.avif?t=1741545119\" width=524 height=398 /></span><br><br><strong>Main features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>20 tunnels to explore.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collection of objects.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 levels of difficulty.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Variety of enemies.</li></ul>",
